{
  "stem": "1062.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were no-- there were no theaters, no restaurant, no-- and so-- so-- you know, they would fight.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "All right, whether it's nice or not nice, but this is how it was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This type of life was going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was quiet.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was nice.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The scenery was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My village is in the foothills of the Carpathian Mountains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And-- and-- and the fields were lush and green and nice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And-- and, you know, we had to go to the forest to-- for-- for-- for wood, to make meals.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And as a child, I would go out in the-- in the-- in the woods and gather-- gather old branches to bring home for my mother to cook because there was no gas over there.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You know, we had to go and gather branches.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the forest didn't really have good wood.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You know, they were poor forests.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But they had a lot of branches, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So I would make bundles and bring it for my mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And this is how she would cook.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But as I say, they were-- because since didn't know any better, they were happy days.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "If I had a new-- a new-- a new pair of pants or a new suit or something like this, it was a big thing.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "You made a-- you made a [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You made a [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was a big-- but most of the time, what happened, it was passed along.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "In other words, I would-- when I grew up, my shirt, I would give it to my-- to my-- to my--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Brothers.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so-- and what they would also do is take-- like, in other words, if you-- if somebody had an old coat, they would take the old coat and turn it inside out so that, you know-- and there were tailors there, you know.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and-- and it was a project.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, just to make a coat, it would take a couple of weeks, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So-- so this is how you-- you had-- you had clothes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother would also make-- they would spin their own-- she would spin her own-- and not only my mother, but the entire village.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They grew flax.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know if you know what flax is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they would put it in the water, soak it in the water.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then-- but it's a whole process to it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then they would break it, and they would make flax and take the flax and put it on a long-- on a long stick, like, you know, on a long stick.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in the end, my mother would have like a spindle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And down at the spindle was a potato in order to-- for balance.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she would go like-- she would go like.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She would-- she-- she-- she-- she would take the-- the flax and pull it like.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- and then she would spin it over here, then pull it, and she would [? spin it. ?] And-- and-- and this is how she would make thread-- thread.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And when she had enough thread, then I would have-- then she would-- I would keep my hands like this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she would put the flax in my both hands because then she had to make rows.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I would keep my hands.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My-- I felt my hands are falling out from my socket because I had to keep it like this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And she would make-- she would make, you know, balls of-- of-- of-- of this--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--material.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then in the wintertime, they would set up like a-- like a--",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
